      "description": "This exceptional vehicle is presented in impeccable showroom condition, representing the absolute zenith of its model year. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine interior upholstery, reflects an uncompromising standard of care and preservation. Historically maintained with precision, this unit offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle that performs and presents as if it were newly commissioned.",
