    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to say goodbye to this beauty, but it's time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it was first driven off the lot! I've babied it since day one, keeping it perfectly clean and garage-kept. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next big adventure. You've seriously got to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Come take it for a spin!",
