    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. This example features the S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve its high-revving 333 hp output. The mechanical pedigree is documented and exhaustive: the subframe has been reinforced with a bespoke plate kit, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M-Variable lock differential. The chassis remains perfectly balanced with refreshed bushings and an uncompromised suspension geometry. This vehicle presents with a flawless underside and zero hydraulic leaks, representing a turn-key acquisition for the purist seeking the zenith of analog M-division engineering.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
